  This is Theorem 30 in <fr:link href="/ref-3RL5/" title="Maximal (sequentially) compact topologies" uri="https://charloced.github.io/ref-3RL5/" display-uri="ref-3RL5" type="local">Reference <fr:contextual-number uri="https://charloced.github.io/ref-3RL5/" display-uri="ref-3RL5" /></fr:link>.
