            <fr:title text="Relative Boolean algebras over a Boolean base are simply Boolean algebras">Relative Boolean algebras over a Boolean base are simply Boolean algebras</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Lemma</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>
  Suppose we have a <fr:link href="/idem-comm-7K36/" title="Relative Boolean algebra" uri="https://charloced.github.io/idem-comm-7K36/" display-uri="idem-comm-7K36" type="local"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[B]]></fr:tex>-Boolean algebra</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[B \to  E]]></fr:tex> with <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[B]]></fr:tex> Boolean. Then this is equivalently simply a Boolean algebra morphism <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[B \to  E]]></fr:tex>. This is because by <fr:link href="/idem-comm-E7E2/" title="Boolean algebras only have maximal ideals" uri="https://charloced.github.io/idem-comm-E7E2/" display-uri="idem-comm-E7E2" type="local">Remark <fr:contextual-number uri="https://charloced.github.io/idem-comm-E7E2/" display-uri="idem-comm-E7E2" /></fr:link>, any quotient <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[J/B]]></fr:tex> for a prime ideal <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[J]]></fr:tex> in <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[B]]></fr:tex> is isomorphic to <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[2]]></fr:tex>, and a non-trivial epimorphism from <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[2]]></fr:tex> must be an isomorphism (cf. <fr:link href="/idem-comm-VEWK/" title="Epimorphisms between distributive lattices" uri="https://charloced.github.io/idem-comm-VEWK/" display-uri="idem-comm-VEWK" type="local">Proposition <fr:contextual-number uri="https://charloced.github.io/idem-comm-VEWK/" display-uri="idem-comm-VEWK" /></fr:link>). This implies all prime ideals of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[E]]></fr:tex> are maximal, hence by <fr:link href="/idem-comm-E7E2/" title="Boolean algebras only have maximal ideals" uri="https://charloced.github.io/idem-comm-E7E2/" display-uri="idem-comm-E7E2" type="local">Remark <fr:contextual-number uri="https://charloced.github.io/idem-comm-E7E2/" display-uri="idem-comm-E7E2" /></fr:link> again <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[E]]></fr:tex> is a Boolean algebra.
</html:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
        </fr:tree>
